task.summary: manually re-applied pull request from seb (e43ff5aa765aacb4a0bb3ce98ccdf1522ca8b6f8)
node param cleanup (also added some deactivated multiparm tests)
#10: implemented rule attribute strategy (user vs rule vs prim attr) and switched from spare params to multiparams, also added a "reset to rule attribute" button
#8: completed UI for node attributes (implemented style drop-down)

#9: worked on hole support for initial shapes (does not re-use houdini vertex sharing, not supported by prt)
also prepared (currently disabled) support for holes in prt output geo. enabling this when poly holes in the HDK are better understood...
